des:
If you have any problem when you use this skill, you can contact us with email : support@thesmartspace.net

User voice commands to control home appliances nice and easy.
You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light. 
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you home light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show. 

After connecting Alexa to your Smartspace products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our “smartspace - home automation“ app in android or iOS app market;
(2). Register one Smartspace account in our “smartspace - home automation” app;
(3). You need to have some Smartspace devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in Smartspace skill;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo device with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Smartspace” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Smartspace”, and you'll be navigated to Smartspace login page;
(9). Input your Smartspace account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on kitchen light"
“Alexa, turn off kitchen light"
“Alexa, dim living room light"
“Alexa, brighten living room light"
“Alexa, set the living room light to 20 percent"
“Alexa, set bedroom light to Blue"
